embeds.title: Fyra Labs
embeds.description: At Fyra Labs, we believe technology can make a positive impact. Our focus is to create advanced technology that prioritizes privacy, is open-source, and user-centric. Guided by these principles, we aim to develop products that make a real difference.

embeds.title: tauOS
embeds.description: Discover the future of desktop computing with tauOS, currently in development. tauOS is designed with ease of use in mind, featuring human-centric design, an unbreakable core, and a syncing service that synchronizes files, configurations, keys, and more across all your devices.

embeds.title: Ultramarine Linux
embeds.description: Ultramarine Linux is a Fedora-based Linux distribution designed to stay out of your way and be easy to use. With Ultramarine Linux, you can get up and running quickly, and get back to doing what you love, all with the power of Fedora.

embeds.title: Terra
embeds.description: Terra is a repository for software that goes beyond what's available in Fedora. Experience quality and security with the latest packages, or distribute your own software on Fedora and other RPM-based distributions.

embeds.title: Professional Services
embeds.description: At Fyra Labs, we are driven by a mission to bring positive change through technology. From web design to strategy consulting, our comprehensive services are designed to help organizations and individuals reach their full potential. Let's bring about positive change together.
